Well, these are jets going at very high speeds, so if they left a
smell, it would be a fuel stench around a very big area.

::Vycir/Flare::

The Vycir jet pulls up, the shockwave from the grenade shaking it. It
gains altitude and then turns, going for another pass from the
opposide side of the Terrorcon group that the other Galactor jet was
coming from.
